tool written in Pharo.

8
00:00:22,490 --> 00:00:25,450
What is interesting is that
it only uses Pharo syntax.

9
00:00:25,790 --> 00:00:27,610
All you will see,
all you will manipulate,

10
00:00:27,777 --> 00:00:28,700
are Pharo expressions.

11
