For example, here, you have
a Pharo comment

12
00:00:32,027 --> 00:00:34,040
that explains to do "Hello"

13
00:00:34,207 --> 00:00:37,120
then, "Select the text",

14
00:00:37,287 --> 00:00:40,020
use right-click and 
choose "do it".

15
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:44,930
We will do it using 
keyboard shortcuts.

16
00:00:47,910 --> 00:00:50,180
Et voilà, I moved to 
the second lesson.

17
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:53,230
Now you understood the principle,

18
00:00:53,397 --> 00:00:56,790
